scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: The ISDA Master Agreement Schedule begins at line 350 ("SCHEDULE") and continues through the end of the schedule's terms, which is line 464 ("[Remainder of Page Intentionally Left Blank.]"). This span includes all the negotiated terms between the parties and excludes the standard pre-printed Master Agreement, definitions, and any annexes such as the CSA. The signature block for the schedule follows at line 465, but the substantive schedule content is lines 350-464.
